{"tid":2399450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"39歲李施嬅手戴巨鑽拖實另一半宣布婚訊：I Said YES！","createTime":"2021-02-08T06:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T09:33:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d69533fa9c6fb9be8bc85d2867ee4dd66ddcf8","tid":2399450,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"恭喜恭喜，正身在加拿大拍攝劇集《Blood and Water》（血與水）第3季嘅李施嬅Selena ，2月8日中午於IG上載一張同男子手拖手，左手無名指手戴巨鑽戒指嘅相，留言話：「I Said Yes.」<br />\n<br />\nSelena上載兩張相，：「牛年一定會更好。因為有這樣的新嘗試🎤，也有甜蜜的新嘗試。Good night .Year of the Ox.New and exciting beginnings.」最重要係Hashtag「#感恩 #blessings #ISaidYES」短短三十分鐘已經超過萬人畀like向佢送上祝福。佢嘅好姐妹胡杏兒表示：「我哋都知道左一段時間啦，好戥佢地開心，好期待佢哋嘅婚禮！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210208/435448766854729728605987.jpeg/lgEF_LX5h4z_uRFxKWHfTQm_JtRSVXskQegba0HoG2s?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210208%2F435448766854729728605987.jpeg%2FlgEF_LX5h4z_uRFxKWHfTQm_JtRSVXskQegba0HoG2s%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1a383d85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"126d692f6dcc4dd0730de453e91c981ace3f0931","tid":2399450,"uid":193098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"劇情需要。。。。刷存在感，啲相俾人知道唔係近日影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5256d84831c3af75c21195cc9753b87dc5260cf","tid":2399450,"uid":68081,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"126d692f6dcc4dd0730de453e91c981ace3f0931","tid":2399450,"uid":193098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"劇情需要。。。。刷存在感，啲相俾人知道唔係近日影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"冇計要見報，起碼好過件煩西胡大媽！生三件關我撚事咩！日日報導"},{"pid":"20d4e7bfc7e841ae0b21f6bd11865e785ba9a69f","tid":2399450,"uid":193098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5256d84831c3af75c21195cc9753b87dc5260cf","tid":2399450,"uid":68081,"like":